						               													<description>In A.D. 2986 people are no longer inhabiting earth which was completely destroyed by climate change. Mankind was forced to look for alternative planets as settlements and eventually spread out over dozens of smaller micro-planets.&amp;#10;The Galaxy Post was founded for the exchange of material things between the planets such as orders, letters and of course bills.&amp;#10;And you're working your first day as a Galaxy Postman today!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Galaxy Postman players are going to deliver packages and giving aliens a lift back home while upgrading their shuttle to better suit their needs!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Every round each player rolls their dice pool and select dice to activate action tiles on their shuttle board.&amp;#10;The Postman will move their shuttle through the galaxy full of dangers to deliver packages, take aliens back to their mothership and upgrade their shuttle to use better actions. Doing so they must always monitor their energy to ensure that it does not suffer system errors.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game ends after a fixed number of rounds, if a postman was able to deliver all his packages or there are too many aliens out in the galaxy still waiting for lift.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
